net.coderodde.stat.support

Class ArrayProbabilityDistribution<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.coderodde.stat.AbstractProbabilityDistribution<E>
      • net.coderodde.stat.support.ArrayProbabilityDistribution<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the actual type of the elements stored in this probability distribution.

    public class ArrayProbabilityDistribution<E>
extends AbstractProbabilityDistribution<E>
    This class implements a probability distribution relying on an array of elements. The running times are as follows:
    Method Complexity
    addElement amortized constant time,
    sampleElement O(n),
    removeElement O(n).
    Version:
    1.61 (Sep 30, 2016)
    Author:
    Rodion "rodde" Efremov
